snippet.title: Go Morse Go! Arcade Edition - First Trailer
snippet.description:
The definitive version of Go Morse Go! is coming soon! Up to 4 players can use their telegraphs to beep the letters that Samantha shouts and build up their hype meters. Go Morse Go! Arcade Edition features new game modes, customizable matches, and 26 different outfits/characters.

Coming to Steam and itch.io later this month!
